title: Unable to recognize/connect to 5ghz Wi-Fi networks in Kazakhstan
content:
This is the original post: My Pixel 3 doesn't support 5GHz WiFi - Pixel Phone Community (google.com)
I want to confirm i have the same issue (unable to detect/see/connect to 5 ghz Wi-Fi networks, 2.4 ghz connection works fine). And it would be really insignificantly easy to complete it as long as it gets in hands of Google Engineers...
